        "content": "# Maestro Context Index\n\n<!-- maestro-setup:generated:start -->\n## Context Files\n\nLoad this file first, then open only the context documents relevant to the task.\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| `architecture.md` | Repo structure, module ownership, and boundaries |\n| `product-sense.md` | Product goals, users, and UX guardrails |\n| `quality-gates.md` | Validation commands and review expectations |\n| `security.md` | Security-sensitive areas and approval gates |\n| `workflow.md` | Human-in-the-loop delivery workflow |\n| `planning.md` | Planning policy and Maestro plan/task bridge |\n| `code_styleguides/` | Detected language style guides |\n\n## Agent Read Order\n\n1. Read root `AGENTS.md`.\n2. Read this index.\n3. Open the smallest relevant set of context files.\n4. Open matching language guides from `code_styleguides/` before code edits.\n\n## Setup State\n\n- Generated by `maestro-setup`.\n- Unknown or weakly inferred facts are marked TODO.\n<!-- maestro-setup:generated:end -->\n\n## User Notes\n\nAdd project-specific notes here. This section is outside the managed block.\n"
