        "path": "reference/context-templates/product-sense.md",
        "content": "# Product Sense Context\n\n<!-- maestro-setup:generated:start -->\n## Product Goal\n\nTODO(maestro-setup): State who this project serves and what outcome it creates.\n\n## Primary Users\n\n- TODO(maestro-setup): Infer or record primary users.\n\n## Product Principles\n\n- Prefer clarity over cleverness.\n- Prefer predictable flows over surprising automation.\n- Make user-visible failures diagnosable.\n- Keep risky decisions explicit.\n\n## UX Guardrails\n\n- Do not introduce hidden destructive behavior.\n- Do not silently change established terms or defaults.\n- Preserve user trust when trading off speed and control.\n<!-- maestro-setup:generated:end -->\n\n## User Notes\n\nAdd product guidance here. This section is outside the managed block.\n"
